How to get to being able to flash Arduino Uno.

Install CLion
Install AVR8 toolchain from https://www.microchip.com/mplab/avr-support/avr-and-arm-toolchains-c-compilers
Install avrdude (ming32) from http://download.savannah.gnu.org/releases/avrdude/
Install PlatformIO via PowerShell and python
Add platformIO scripts folder to system path variable
Make new CLion project from platformio > arduino menu
Add a CMakeListsUser.txt in root to include specific bits
Add toolchain with build tool being mingw32-make.exe in appdata toolbox folder
    compilers and debuggers from downloaded toolchain

Go!
